          <button class="template-btn" onclick="useTemplate('Thank you for your feedback! We truly appreciate hearing from you and would love the opportunity to make things right. Please call us at [YOUR_PHONE] at your convenience.')">
            üôè Thank you & make it right
          </button>
          <button class="template-btn" onclick="useTemplate('We\'re sorry to hear about your experience. Your feedback is important to us. Could you please reach out to us directly so we can resolve this? [YOUR_PHONE]')">
            üíî Apologize & invite contact
          </button>
          <button class="template-btn" onclick="useTemplate('Hi! We noticed your feedback and want to ensure you had a great experience. Please let us know if there\'s anything we can do to help!')">
            üëã Follow-up check-in
          </button>
